"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Plain lateral functional x-rays in flexion (A) and extension (B), showing hypermobility and spondylolisthesis at the Th11/12 level. Especially in flexion, severe kyphosis and spondylolisthesis were accompanied by sinking of the upper vertebra. Sagittal computed tomography scan (C) shows marginal bone sclerosis. Magnetic resonance imaging (D) shows the mass intensity is likely vertebral disc.",
